            <abstract>
                <p>A collection of St George texts with fixed content and (more or less) stable
                    sequence in its manuscript transmission: after the <ref type="work"
                        corresp="LIT6210MGTranslatio"/>, 12 miracles, classified by Budge as
                    canonical, follow in a (more or less fixed) sequence, (possibly?) assigned for
                    the 7th of Ḫǝdār. All these texts were translated by <bibl>
                        <ptr target="bm:Budge1930George"/>
                    </bibl> based on <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient691"/>.</p>
            </abstract>

